title: Donald Trump Embraces 4Chan Fans, Retweets Absurd Dubstep “You Can’t Stump The Trump” Video
text:
0 Comment 
Impressed by his attitude, 4chan.org, the website which originally gave birth to the online Anonymous movement, has declared Donald Trump to be "the first meme president." The site's "politically incorrect" politics message board has been described as "racist" by the Southern Poverty Law Center, but it went wild when Donald Trump retweeted a link to a video made by one of their own called: "You Can't Stump The Trump (vol. 4)," a compilation of his greatest debate moments set to dubstep music.
